table_description: AWS VPC Elastic IP Address Transfer

columns.name: allocation_id
columns.description: The allocation ID of an Elastic IP address.

columns.name: address_transfer_status
columns.description: The Elastic IP address transfer status.

columns.name: public_ip
columns.description: The Elastic IP address being transferred.

columns.name: transfer_account_id
columns.description: The ID of the account that you want to transfer the Elastic IP address to.

columns.name: transfer_offer_accepted_timestamp
columns.description: The timestamp when the Elastic IP address transfer was accepted.

columns.name: transfer_offer_expiration_timestamp
columns.description: The timestamp when the Elastic IP address transfer expired.
